Package: stwd
Title: Storytelling with Data Visualizations for ggplot2
Version: 3.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alejandro", "Hagan", , "alejandro.hagan@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create presentation-ready visualizations following Storytelling
    with Data (SWD) principles. Provides story layouts that combine charts
    with narrative text, colored titles, and supporting context. Includes an
    interactive Shiny app for designing layouts, strategic color highlighting,
    and integration with the marquee package for colored text labels.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
